{"tid":379953,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【處女改詞招唱】毒撚最鍾意既就係FF","createTime":"2017-08-29T17:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T10:04:57.000Z","uid":2350,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1141075c02fce3569b56fdf7db39defb0ba470","tid":379953,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/011546_5a28ae7676c35f9b63dd8ec9500d8567.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F011546_5a28ae7676c35f9b63dd8ec9500d8567.png&h=425511ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「男人唔係從不主動，而係成日都蠢蠢欲動」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年改呢首詞果陣自覺感情豐富，今日咁啱睇返剩係睇倒一片柒味。<br />\n雖然係咁，都想幫佢搵個歸宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原曲：那些年<br />\n作詞：九把刀<br />\n作曲：木村充利<br />\n改詞：凱笑<br />\n<br />\n<strong>難忘妳轉角那身影<br />\n不經意見妳正孤身<br />\n一剎掠過願再會亦無期<br />\n流連在街頭故地<br />\n尋找當天的妳<br />\n那夜我終找到妳心終可暗喜 <br />\n<br />\n夜靜妳獨坐在角落<br />\n膽忽壯坐到妳對面<br />\n只盼讓我伴妳同遊一晚<br />\n轉過面妳眼色太動人<br />\n如像妳看的是情人<br />\n卻沒法把這交談變做答允<br />\n<br />\n心聲不堪等未開口竟破碎<br />\n傻笑著呆望妳漸醉<br />\n卻只得到似雪婉絕<br />\n這晚再見未挽手<br />\n而妳心不願留<br />\n對望無言說悶轉身走<br />\n<br />\n明明未說與我同遊<br />\n然而我偏不想獨奏<br />\n妳今雖遠去　<br />\n再遇見亦能旁觀<br />\n從來未寄望有終點<br />\n我仍求能曾守護妳<br />\n偏起跑線亦難覓如水中泡影<br />\n<br />\n從來未看破這離愁<br />\n然而我今天需獨奏<br />\n妳身影遠去　<br />\n角落那動人舊身影<br />\n重頭回望從未怕累<br />\n心終碎淚難收心裡<br />\n假使可再遇如何能悲中帶喜<br />\n我怕遇上妳<br />\n<br />\n難忘妳轉角那身影<br />\n今竟見妳笑語燦爛<br />\n可笑是我又盼能談一晚<br />\n不轉面妳看他太入神<br />\n凝望妳眼心再下沉<br />\n眼眸裡只見他和妳在靠近<br />\n<br />\n心聲不肯等未得到竟遠去<br />\n傻笑但無力去面對<br />\n妳會跟他每晚安睡<br />\n再見妳已在挽手<br />\n而我心那可留<br />\n妳漸模糊眼淚已失守<br />\n<br />\n明明未說與我同遊<br />\n然而我偏不想獨奏<br />\n與他早遠去　<br />\n卻剩我默然旁觀<br />\n原來是我在這終點<br />\n看著那旁人守護妳<br />\n孤身一個如何問愁思怎去掩<br />\n<br />\n從來未看破這離愁<br />\n然而我今天需獨奏<br />\n妳身影遠去　<br />\n角落那動人舊身影<br />\n重頭回望從未怕累<br />\n心終碎淚難收心裡<br />\n不敢想故地重遇如今只有悲<br />\n我怕未放棄</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既朋友可以like下我個facebook page，話唔定有驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hoisiuaiioh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhoisiuaiioh%2F&d=pjaYt0RjaqmNpsRvj%2FdAASwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=21005257\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hoisiuaiioh/</a>"},{"pid":"c9e1a46912ea99aa222a8444fe5628eb1fa071ee","tid":379953,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:25:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9531530dc94397e134a2a9b3031aac863e93677","tid":379953,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"呢排大家鍾意復古？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d13a83a8589185ff661ea6dbf27da474b6d5bb","tid":379953,"uid":122380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"處女詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1541f22fe132f842746c0349d9553ca2bd8d3c9","tid":379953,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>處女詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔記得加[有圖]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8c22580d03959fb0ef8f946295ecf65ce3b24e","tid":379953,"uid":2350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排大家鍾意復古？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歷史係應該沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/